Introduce local for 'this' is not very useful

**Version Used**: VS 15.7

**Steps to Reproduce**:

1. Move caret to `this` and press `Ctrl+.`

```C#
	sealed class C {
		readonly string s;
		public C(string s) {
			this.s = s;
